/>\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('26','','','','<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">The brands of TRANSSION HOLDINGS are attractive and desirable. Of course, that is a good thing – but it also has its downsides.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">Over recent years, illegal production and global sales of fake TECNO phones and accessories have increased dramatically. A quick bargain soon reveals its inferior quality&nbsp;which will cause&nbsp;a safety hazard. The economic damage is extensive.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">The best way to protect yourself from counterfeit products is to go to your local authorised TECNO, itel or Infinix dealers or Carlcare Service Centres to buy products, spare parts and accessories or to&nbsp;seek their advices.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">Product piracy prevails in many sectors – not just in&nbsp;software, watches, designer clothing, medications , but also in the mobile industry, from spare parts to complete phones.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">It is the aim of TRANSSION HOLDINGS to minimise the consequential risks and dangers for its customers.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">The illegal production and corresponding global sales of forged goods are continuously increasing.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">These also include</span> \n	</p>\n	<blockquote>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">-&nbsp;Original TECNO mobile phone</span> \n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">-&nbsp;Original TECNO accessories</span> \n		</p>\n	</blockquote>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">What appears at first glance to be a bargain often proves to be an inferior quality imitation.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">Yet the loss caused to the consumer by fake products is usually greater than the expected saving.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>','2','?tag=26','/uploads/13993688695739.jpg','','/uploads/13995188048980.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('27','Infinix','Infinix','','<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><strong></strong></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><strong>Infinix Mobility,</strong> a member of Transsion group, since its creation in 2009, has become a major player in the smartphones and tablets market. Avant-garde designs, innovative functions and impeccable quality are just some of the reasons why millions of consumers are attracted to our products every year.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">With the brand spirit of “challenging the norms”, Infinix smart devices are designed specifically for young generations who want to stand out, reach out and&nbsp;be&nbsp;in sync with the world. Provide high-quality intelligence products with our consumers to create a distinctive smart lifestyle.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">At the cutting edge of innovation in the wireless mobile Internet domain, Infinix defies the norms and opens the doors to the future!</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>','2','?tag=27','/images/infinix2.jpg','','/images/banner_infinix2.jpg','')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('28','iFLUX','iFLUX','iFLUX','<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\">\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\"><strong>iFLUX</strong> is a professional LED lighting brand of TRANSSION HOLDINGS.</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">Staying true to the maxim \"think globally, act locally\", iFLUX aims to transform advanced LED lighting technology into superior localized products.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align:justify;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">Meanwhile, iFLUX puts&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"text-align:justify;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">heavy consideration&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">on customer experience and endeavors to provide consumers with the most suitable LED lighting products by adopting the latest innovative technology.</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">iFLUX possesses a comprehensive product portfolio, including indoor lights, outdoor lights, solar-powered lights, portable lamps and rechargeable system, etc. The core value of iFLUX&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">products&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">is&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">\"Quality Light, Quality Life\". With strong R&amp;D and manufacturing ability, iFLUX provides customers with LED lighting products of reliable quality, reasonable prices and great</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">comfort.</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">Applying the \"Whole-Procedure Quality Inspection and Controlling\" from R&amp;D to manufacture, owning efficient logistics and distribution system and offering professional after-sale service&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">based on&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">Carlcare, iFLUX can do the best in each link of a product cycle in this industry.</span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;\">Undoubtedly, iFLUX will be the fastest developing LED lighting brand in Africa and will become the most popular lighting brand among African consumers.</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<span style=\"white-space:nowrap;\"></span></span>','2','?tag=28','/uploads/14440272361136.jpg','','/uploads/14440272322194.jpg','')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('31','Operating System','Operating System','Operating System','<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:nowrap;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Excellence Comes as Standard</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;\">· </span></strong></span></span>After years of development, TRANSSION has formed a relatively mature operating system, including Human Resource Management System, Financial Management System, Marketing Management System, Production and Quality Management System and Supply Chain Management System.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#666666;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;\">· </span></strong></span></span>With years of exploitation and summarizing, TRANSSION has built up a one-stop service system, which embraces chip support, main board R&amp;D, supply chain management, new product R&amp;D,&nbsp; production, branding and marketing, channel development, product distribution and customer service.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><br />\n</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>','3','?tag=31','','','/uploads/13993685748361.png','<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('32','研究开发','研究开发','研究开发','<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">Research and Development as an important part of its strategic development, TRANSSION HOLDINGS has built up a market-driven and customer-oriented research and development mode to provide customers with innovative products that meet their needs.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">The company has its own R&amp;D labs for design in France and China to make sure that its handsets are always on the cutting edge of the world\'s trends.</span> \n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">Meanwhile, we have brought in a group of world top talents in software and hardware technology with their years of experience in this field. Thanks to its own R&amp;D center with continuous input and scientific innovation system, TRANSSION HOLDINGS&nbsp;guarantees that its products always are with world-class quality. Now its products are favored by customers with its reliable quality and fashionable design.</span> \n		</p>','3','?tag=32','/uploads/13994520984265.jpg','','/uploads/13994520866111.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><br />\n</span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('33','供应链管理','供应链管理','供应链管理','<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">Each of the suppliers has been carefully selected by TRANSSION HOLDINGS, as we consider every supplier as a part of us and each part is crucial for high quality. TRANSSION has set up a quality management system with a strict quality standard&nbsp;for all incoming materials.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS has been building strong and close relationships with top suppliers all over the world to achieve mutual development.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">With a cross-platform information system, we share information together, which makes sure that the information in the system is accurate and delivered timely and guarantees the smooth operation of all business processes. Only with joint efforts with its partners in supply chain, can the products of TRANSSION HOLDINGS&nbsp;be favored by consumers all the time.</span> \n</p>','3','?tag=33','/uploads/13993577429266.jpg','','/uploads/13993577364960.jpg','<p style=\"white-space:normal;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div>\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><br />\n</span> \n</div>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('34','','','','<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">How to be our supplier?</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS always puts priority on quality of mobile phone, that’s why we are looking forward to cooperate with the best supplier who is able to tie with international rivals and pursue sustainable development as well. Our suppliers gave us a great support by providing innovative products, reliable services, on time delivery, and the market pricing, etc. In return, we have established a long-term cooperative partnership of equality and mutual benefit with them.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">Do you want to be supplier of TRANSSION HOLIDNGS? If you meet the basic requirements below, you are welcome to send the information of your company to this email address purchase@transsion.com.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><strong>Basic requirements for the product and brand:</strong></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">1. Have a good brand reputation and certain popularity in the industry;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">2.&nbsp; Excellent product quality; and manufacturers should have strict product quality control system;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">3. Manufacturer should have perfect sale and after-sale service;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">4. Products are required to meet all kinds of mandatory standard (we require the certificates of CE, ROSH, etc.).</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><strong>Basic requirements to suppliers:</strong></span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">1. Provide a competitive price and policies to guarantee sufficient capacity and stable supply;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">2.&nbsp; Accept payment on term or bank acceptance;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">3.&nbsp; Agencies need to provide the valid authorization files of the product, while manufacturers need to provide the trademark registration of its products</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">4. Offer valid company documents (such as business license, tax registration certificate, and organization code certificate);</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">5.&nbsp; Have the general taxpayer qualification; for all the supply of products, can provide value-added tax invoices, the content of which should be in consistent with the actual purchase goods;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">6.&nbsp; Provide a good support of after-sale service.</span> \n	</p>\n<br />\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<div>\n	</div>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>','3','?tag=34','/uploads/13993547793123Apply-to-Be-a-Supplier_s.jpg','','/uploads/13993547724967Apply-to-Be-a-Supplier.jpg','<p style=\"white-space:normal;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:31.81818199157715px;line-height:58.18181610107422px;white-space:normal;\"> </span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n	<strong style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><br />\n</strong> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<div>\n	<br />\n</div>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('35','生产制造','生产制造','生产制造','<div>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Production Base</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS owns a production base, covering more than 20000 square meters after expanded extensively for three times, with a total head count of over 2000 and production lines of over 40. Now it has become one of the best production bases in China. All the factories have adopted \"7S” management system to create a safe, clean and orderly production environment to ensure high production efficiency.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">In order to meet its need of sustainable development, TRANSSION HOLDINGS is planning to further enlarge its production base, making it as one of the largest and best professional products bases.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Production Capacity</span> \n		</p>\n		<p>\n			<span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">With its huge production capacity, the production base with top manufacturing equipment can produce nearly 150,000 handsets daily and over 30,000,000 handsets annually, providing great support for all brands with high quality products.</span> \n		</p>\n			</div>','3','?tag=35','/uploads/13993720245896.jpg','','/uploads/13993719787006.jpg','<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('36','','','','<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">“Quality Always”</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS pays great attention to its product quality. \"Quality always\" has always been the motto of the company.</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">The company has a quality management system (QMS). There are more than 200 quality personnel doing thorough inspections over 168 items within the whole quality control process. </span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">With the powerful quality assurance system and experienced quality control team, TRANSSION is doing its best in every segment to ensure the high quality of its products. TRANSSION makes nothing but the world-class products for the market. </span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/1399434483.jpg\" /> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Quality Certificate</span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;\"></span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#666666;font-size:13px;\"></span></span>&nbsp;\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">All TECNO products have gained SGS ISO9000 international quality certificate and now apply for ISO14000 and ISO18000 certificate. And TRANSSION HOLDINGS has become Customs A Class Enterprise and Second-class Enterprise in Commodity Inspection. Besides, we has been building strong and close relationships with top suppliers, including Huaqin, Longcheer, Ruijiake, Sajitong and MTK, etc., all over the world to provide customers with world-class products.</span></span> \n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:normal;\">\n		<img alt=\"\" src=\"/uploads/1399435621.jpg\" /> \n	</p>\n	<div>\n		<br />\n	</div>\n	<p style=\"white-space:normal;\">\n		<br />\n	</p>\n	<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n		<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>','3','?tag=36','/uploads/13993556786219quality-system_s.jpg','','/uploads/13993720484529.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;white-space:normal;\">\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('37','','','','<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Channel Building</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<a></a><a></a><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">A large and flexible sales network is the core competitiveness of a company and plays an important role in&nbsp;the company.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS takes the national dealers as the main line, and provincial dealers the base, taking root in Africa. After years of effort, it has built up a large sales network in over 20 countries in Africa, including Nigeria, Kenya, Tanzania, Uganda, Ghana, Ethiopia, Mali, and Cameroon, etc.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Brand Building</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">Since its foundation, TRANSSION HOLDINGS pays great attention in brand building to strengthen the company’s core competitiveness. All the three brands of this company have gained its success with their outstanding and unique marketing strategies and have become significant parts of the mobile industry in Africa.</span> \n	</p>\n	<p>\n		<br />\n	</p>','3','?tag=37','/uploads/13993624728534.jpg','','/uploads/13993624669724.jpg','<p>\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('38','Customer Service','Customer Service','Customer Service','<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<a></a><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Your Satisfaction is Our Priority</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">Excellent after-sales service ensures good sales volumes.</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS regards every sold products as a part of the business operation and strives to ensure that every our customer can get favorable service.</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:28px;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;\"></span></span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:28px;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;\">We have the largest after-sales network providing the best service in Africa.&nbsp;Currently, there are over&nbsp;<strong>80</strong> Carlcare Service Centres in Africa, and more new centres are under construction. We have more than&nbsp;<strong>800&nbsp;</strong>professional employees providing our customers with great service<strong>.</strong></span> </span>\n</p>','3','?tag=38','/uploads/13993749334869.jpg','','/uploads/13992760038364customer service.jpg','<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"font-size:32px;line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<br />')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('41','Careers','Careers','Careers','<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;\"><span style=\"line-height:58px;\"></span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<br />\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Design&nbsp;Your Career, Create Your Life</span> \n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:12px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:12px;\"><strong style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:32px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:12px;\"></span></strong></span></span>\n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\"><strong style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:32px;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';white-space:normal;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:14px;\">·&nbsp; </span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">Everything starts with passion&nbsp;in TRANSSION HOLDINGS</span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:14px;\">. It turns a job into a career. It drives us to&nbsp;turn challenges&nbsp;into opportunities&nbsp;and bring innovative ideas into action.</span></span> \n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">· </span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;Enthusiasm for mobile communication turns a team into a strong unit where every opinion is valued.</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">· </span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;It is only when expertise, highly professional processes and enjoyment of work are united that we can shape the future together.</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#666666;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">·&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;No matter what are you looking forward to in </span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS</span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-size:14px;\">, you can share your professional passion with us and find your future here.</span></span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:9pt;\"></span></b> \n</p>','4','?tag=41','','','/uploads/13992760212143careers.jpg','')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('42','','','','<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Together, We Can</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">TRANSSION HOLDINGS has always endeavored for the satisfaction of all its shareholders, business partners and all members from TRANSSION HOLDINGS family with transparent and effective management and consistent self-renovation. </span>\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;\">With the core value “TOGETHER, WE CAN\", TRANSSION HOLDINGS&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;\">and most of its business partners coexist harmoniously and have all achieved great success. Facing fierce market competition, TRANSSION HOLDINGS</span><span style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;white-space:normal;font-size:14px;\">&nbsp;insists on the same spirit and believes that we will always maintain a win-win business.</span><br />\n</span>\n</p>','1','?tag=42','/uploads/13996287668403.jpg','','/uploads/13996286859466.jpg','<p>\n	<span style=\"text-align:justify;white-space:normal;font-size:32px;font-family:Tahoma;line-height:2;\"> </span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>')
INSERT INTO transsion_info_en VALUES('43','可持续健康发展','可持续健康发展','可持续健康发展','<p>\n	<span style=\"text-align:justify;line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#666666;font-size:32px;\">Sustainable Healthy Development</span> \n</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Tahoma;color:#000000;font-size:14px;\">In the process of seeking its own survival and sustainable development, TRANSSION HOLDINGS adheres to the business philosophy of \"Sustainable Healthy Development\", to achieve both the current business goals and the improvement of the company’s quality, and also to strive to always maintain the continued profitable growth and ability improvement, ensuring a long-term prosperity for the company in the future.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<br />\n</p>','1','?tag=43','/uploads/13993483456478business philosophy-s.jpg','','/uploads/13993660819280.jpg','')
