le team leader experience is preferred.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">3. &nbsp; Be able to work under</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"> press</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">ure；</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\">in</span></span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;\">depende</span><span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">nt problem solving capability.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">4. &nbsp; Strong communication skills, good written &amp; oral ability and management capability.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><strong>Contacts——Tel：0755-33979200&nbsp;&nbsp; E-mail：<a href=\"mailto:hr.hq@transsion.com\">hr.hq@transsion.com</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;\n</p>','0','2014-05-17 08:00:00','','IT','social')
