</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">4. Good communication skills and strong team work spirit.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"line-height:1.5;font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\">5. Send your resume with your satisfied design; take your design at our interview.</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;\n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"><strong>Contacts——Tel：0755-33979200&nbsp;&nbsp; E-mail：<a href=\"mailto:hr.hq@transsion.com\">hr.hq@transsion.com</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Tahoma;font-size:14px;\"></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n	&nbsp;\n</p>','0','2014-04-25 17:46:51','','Design','social')
